==English==
===Intransitive verb===
'''to scud'''
# to [[race]] along [[swiftly]] (especially used of [[cloud]]s)
#{{nautical}} to run before a high [[wind]] with no [[sail]]s set

===Noun===
'''scud'''
# the act of [[scudding]]
